# ai (local)
# ====================================================================
# AI assistants & tooling — combined template
# Cobre Cursor, Claude Code, Aider, OpenAI Codex, GitHub Copilot,
# Continue.dev, Windsurf, Zed AI e artefatos genéricos de IA.
# Mantém arquivos compartilháveis (rules, prompts, AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md)
# e ignora apenas dados locais, históricos de chat, caches e logs.

# --- Cursor (https://cursor.com) ----------------------------------
# Mantém .cursor/rules/, .cursor/commands/ e .cursor/mcp.json (commit)
.cursor/agent-transcripts/
.cursor/logs/
.cursor/state/
.cursor/cache/
.cursor/projects/
.cursor/tmp/
.cursor/*.log

# --- Claude Code (Anthropic) --------------------------------------
# Mantém CLAUDE.md, .claude/settings.json, hooks/, commands/, agents/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/projects/
.claude/state/
.claude/logs/
.claude/cache/
.claude/history/
.claude/.session*
.claude/*.local.*

# --- Aider (https://aider.chat) -----------------------------------
# Mantém .aider.conf.yml (configuração compartilhada)
.aider*
!.aider.conf.yml
!.aider.conf.yaml
.aider.tags.cache.v*/
.aider.chat.history.md
.aider.input.history
.aider.llm.history

